select distinct raum
from IDNR_ZUSATZ iz WITH(NOLOCK)
INNER JOIN dbo.GERAETE g WITH(NOLOCK) on g.Ebene1=iz.Ebene1 and g.Ebene2=iz.Ebene2 and g.Ebene3=iz.Ebene3 and g.Ebene4=iz.Ebene4 and g.IDNR=iz.IDNR INNER JOIN dbo.SM_KONTAKT_KUNDE smk WITH(NOLOCK) on smk.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and smk.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and smk.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and smk.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and smk.KDNR=g.Betreiber and smk.Projekt=:5 and smk.EmailAdresse=':6' and smk.Aktiv=1
WHERE g.Ebene1=:1 and g.Ebene2=:2 and g.Ebene3=:3 and g.Ebene4=:4 and iz.Raum>''
